{
  "texts": [
    "However, these studies lack a control group.",
    "Coming next to proper RCTs, we again find that the majority of works focus on Programming Education.",
    "Lyu et al. (2024), Li et al. (2024) and Pankiewicz and Baker (2024) all found that the treatment group using GenAI tutors benefited over the control group.",
    "However, Choudhuri et al. (2023) and Naik et al. (2024) found no significant differences in their metrics of interest.",
    "Shanshan and Sen (2024) concluded that significant learning gains fade with increasing abstraction levels."
  ]
}